Usage: ast [options] file
Options:
  -h, --help		Display this information and exit
  -v, --version		Display version information and exit
  -V, --verbose		Verbosity has no effect at this time
  -B, --directory <dir>	Changes the resource directory to <dir>
  -a, --compile-all	Compiles into a static library
  -k, --keep-int	Doesn't remove intermediary files with --compile-all
  --clean		Removes all intermediary files left by --keep-int and exit
  -o <file>		Place the output of --compile-all into <file>

For bug reporting instructions, please go fuck yourself.
